                                                                                                   throws org.planit.exceptions.PlanItException
        Create and register a new link segment February 2020: We do not understand how the flow times for link types 1 and 2 are calculated. Link type 3 is the only one for which our results match the published results.
        Parameters:
        network - the current macroscopic network
        link - the current link
        maxSpeed - the maximum speed for this link
        capacityPerLane - the capacity per lane for this link
        linkSegmentTypeExternalId - the external Id of the type of this link segment
        externalId - external Id of this link segment
        length - the length of this link segment
        freeFlowTravelTime - the free flow travel time for this link segment
        Returns:
        the macroscopic link segment which has been created
        Throws:
        org.planit.exceptions.PlanItException - thrown if there is an error
